<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero__container">
    <div class="hero__split-layout">
      <!-- Left side: Large video -->
      <div class="hero__left">
        <div class="hero__video-container">
          <video class="hero__tree-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
            <source src="/images/imagetree.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            <div class="hero__tree-logo">🌳</div>
          </video>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__left-text">
          <h2 class="hero__location-text">岡山から、<br>より良い未来を<br>少しずつ形にしていく。</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side: Content -->
      <div class="hero__right">
        <h1 class="hero__title">TEDx Tsushima <span class="hero__youth">Youth</span></h1>
        <div class="hero__theme-box">
          <p class="hero__theme">Protopia: Roots for Well-being, Innovation</p>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__date-section">
          <div class="hero__year">2025</div>
          <div class="hero__date">12/20</div>
          <div class="hero__venue-box">
            <p>@岡山大学<br>共育共創コモンズ</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__description-sections">
          <div class="hero__description-item">
            <h3>--- What is TEDx ?</h3>
            <p>TEDの理念に共感し、地域発のアイデアを世界に共有するためのプラットフォーム。<br>Ideas worth Spreading.（アイデアは広める価値がある。）という考え方のもと、地域から発信していくことの重要性を強調しています。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hero__description-item">
            <h3>--- What is Youth ?</h3>
            <p>TEDxの中でも、中高生をはじめとする10代の若者が主役のTEDxはTEDx Youthとして開催できます。<br>岡山の若者が、岡山の地から、発信するアイデアにきっと驚かされます。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hero__description-item">
            <h3>--- What is Protopia ?</h3>
            <p>Protopiaとは、ユートピアでもディストピアでもなく、一歩ずつ良くしていく未来のことです。<br>遠い未来をデザインするのではなく、現代に視点を置き、改善を繰り返していく未来のことです。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__join-button" id="heroJoinButton">
          <a href="/join" class="btn btn--join">JOIN</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero__particles" id="heroParticles"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--tedx-white);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 2s ease;
  }

  .hero.red-background {
    background: var(--tedx-red);
    color: var(--tedx-white);
  }

  .hero.red-background .hero__title,
  .hero.red-background .hero__theme,
  .hero.red-background .hero__location-text,
  .hero.red-background .hero__description-item h3,
  .hero.red-background .hero__description-item p,
  .hero.red-background .hero__year,
  .hero.red-background .hero__date,
  .hero.red-background .hero__venue-box p {
    color: var(--tedx-white);
  }

  .hero__container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero__split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  .hero__left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .hero__video-container {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero__tree-video {
    width: 100% !important;
    max-width: 500px !important;
    height: auto !important;
    aspect-ratio: 1 !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero__tree-logo {
    font-size: 200px;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .hero__location-text {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--tedx-black);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero__right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .hero__title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--tedx-black);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero__youth {
    color: var(--tedx-red);
  }

  .hero__theme-box {
    background: rgba(230, 43, 30, 0.95);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1px;
    display: inline-block;
    max-width: 90%;
    min-height: 35px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .hero__theme {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  .hero__date-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    align-self: flex-end;
  }

  .hero__year {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--tedx-red);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero__date {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--tedx-red);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero__venue-box {
    border: 3px solid var(--tedx-red);
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero__venue-box p {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--tedx-black);
  }

  .hero__description-sections {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero__description-item {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero__description-item h3 {
    color: var(--tedx-red);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: #333;
    color: var(--tedx-red);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .hero__description-item p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .hero__join-button {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
    display: none;
  }

  .hero__join-button.show {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
    display: block;
  }

  .hero__particles {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero__split-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero__right {
      padding-left: 0;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero__tree-video {
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .hero__tree-logo {
      font-size: 100px;
    }

    .hero__title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero__location-text {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero__date-section {
      align-self: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero__year {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero__date {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
